data.description: Come see this gorgeous, full brick home! Less than 5 years old. Home offers open floor plan, kitchen with a large island and beautiful granite. Great for entertaining! Home has 4 bedrooms, 3 baths with isolated master suite. Stove, microwave, and dishwasher approx 2 years old. Home offers fenced in back yard and conveniently located to the neighborhood pool and pavilion! **Security System and Refrigerator convey!** Seller also offering a 1 Year home warranty with accepted offer!!
